Class Response

  • java.lang.Object
    • hippodrome.responses.Response
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Response
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Class that provides the needed marshalling options to enable the correct return values for each entity's state changes and actual return values.
